rea_total_km2          = 103.2\n| area_note               =\n| elevation_footnotes     =\n| elevation_m             =\n| population_footnotes    = <ref>[http://www.stat.si/ObcineVStevilkah/Vsebina.aspx?leto=2013&id=192&lang=eng Statistical Office of the Republic of Slovenia]</ref>\n| population_total        = 4190\n| population_as_of        = 2011\n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| population_demonym      =\n| population_note         =\n| timezone1               = [[Central European Time|CET]]\n| utc_offset1             = +01\n| timezone1_DST           = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset1_DST         = +02\n| postal_code_type        =\n| postal_code             = \n| area_code_type          =\n| area_code               =\n| iso_code                =\n| website                 = {{Official URL}}\n| footnotes               =\n}}\nThe '''Municipality of Velike La\u0161\u010de''' ({{IPA-sl|\u02c8\u028be\u02d0lik\u025b \u02c8la\u02d0\u0283t\u0283\u025b|pron}}; {{lang-sl|Ob\u010dina Velike La\u0161\u010de}}) is a [[municipality]] in [[Slovenia]]. The seat of the municipality is the town of [[Velike La\u0161\u010de]]. It is part of the traditional region of [[Lower Carniola]] and is now included in the [[Central Slovenia Statistical Region]].\n\nThe area is the birthplace of a number of notable Slovene writers: [[Primo\u017e Trubar]], [[Josip Stritar]], [[Fran Levstik]], and [[Jo\u017ee Javor\u0161ek]].<ref>[http://www.velike-lasce.si Velike La\u0161\u010de municipal site]</ref>\n\n==Settlements==\nIn addition to the municipal seat of Velike La\u0161\u010de, the municipality also includes the following settlements:\n{{Div col|colwidth=14em}}\n*[[Adamovo, Slovenia|Adamovo]]\n*[[Bane, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Bane]]\n*[[Bavdek]]\n*[[Borovec pri Karlovici]]\n*[[Bo\u0161tetje]]\n*[[Brankovo]]\n*[[Brlog, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Brlog]]\n*[[Bukovec, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Bukovec]]\n*[[Centa, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Centa]]\n*[[\u010cete\u017e pri Turjaku]]\n*[[Dednik]]\n*[[Dolenje Kali\u0161\u010de]]\n*[[Dolnje Retje]]\n*[[Dol\u0161\u010daki]]\n*[[Dvorska Vas, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Dvorska Vas]]\n*[[Gorenje Kali\u0161\u010de]]\n*[[Gornje Retje]]\n*[[Grade\u017e, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Grade\u017e]]\n*[[Gradi\u0161\u010de, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Gradi\u0161\u010de]]\n*[[Grm, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Grm]]\n*[[Hleb\u010de]]\n*[[Hrustovo]]\n*[[Jaki\u010devo]]\n*[[Javorje, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Javorje]]\n*[[Kaplanovo]]\n*[[Karlovica]]\n*[[Knej]]\n*[[Kot pri Veliki Slevici]]\n*[[Krkovo pri Karlovici]]\n*[[Krvava Pe\u010d]]\n*[[Kukmaka]]\n*[[Laporje, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Laporje]]\n*[[Laze, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Laze]]\n*[[Logarji]]\n*[[Lu\u017earji]]\n*[[Ma\u010dki]]\n*[[Mala Slevica]]\n*[[Male La\u0161\u010de]]\n*[[Mali Lo\u010dnik]]\n*[[Mali Osolnik]]\n*[[Marin\u010dki]]\n*[[Medvedjek, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Medvedjek]]\n*[[Mohorje]]\n*[[Naredi]]\n*[[Opalkovo]]\n*[[Osredek, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Osredek]]\n*[[Pe\u010dki]]\n*[[Plosovo]]\n*[[Podhojni Hrib]]\n*[[Podkogelj]]\n*[[Podkraj, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Podkraj]]\n*[[Podlog, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Podlog]]\n*[[Podsmreka pri Velikih La\u0161\u010dah]]\n*[[Podstrmec]]\n*[[Podulaka]]\n*[[Pod\u017eaga]]\n*[[Polzelo]]\n*[[Poznikovo]]\n*[[Prazniki]]\n*[[Prhajevo]]\n*[[Prilesje, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Prilesje]]\n*[[Purka\u010de]]\n*[[Pu\u0161\u010de]]\n*[[Ra\u0161ica, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Ra\u0161ica]]\n*[[Rob, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Rob]]\n*[[Rupe, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Rupe]]\n*[[\u0160\u010durki]]\n*[[Sekiri\u0161\u010de]]\n*[[Selo pri Robu]]\n*[[\u0160kamevec]]\n*[[\u0160krlovica]]\n*[[Sloka Gora]]\n*[[Srnjak]]\n*[[Srobotnik pri Velikih La\u0161\u010dah]]\n*[[Stope, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Stope]]\n*[[Strletje]]\n*[[Strmec, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Strmec]]\n*[[Toma\u017eini]]\n*[[Turjak]]\n*[[Ulaka, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Ulaka]]\n*[[Uzmani]]\n*[[Velika Slevica]]\n*[[Veliki Lo\u010dnik]]\n*[[Veliki Osolnik]]\n*[[Vrh, Velike La\u0161\u010de|Vrh]]\n*[[\u017daga, Velike La\u0161\u010de|\u017daga]] \n*[[Zgon\u010de]] \n{{Div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{commonscat-inline|Velike La\u0161\u010de municipality|Municipality of Velike La\u0161\u010de}}\n*[http://www.geopedia.si/#T105_F408:134_x468523_y78524.5_s12_b4 Municipality of Velike La\u0161\u010de on Geopedia]\n*[http://www.velike-lasce.si/ Municipality of Velike La\u0161\u010de website]\n\n{{Geographic location\n | Centre = Velike La\u0161\u010de\n | N  = [[Municipality of Ig|Ig]] / [[Municipality of \u0160kofljica|\u0160kofljica]]\n | NE = [[Municipality of Grosuplje|Grosuplje]]\n | E  = [[Municipality of Dobrepolje|Dobrepolje]]\n | SE = [[Municipality of Ribnica|Ribnica]]\n | S  = [[Municipality of Sodra\u017eica|Sodra\u017eica]]\n | SW = [[Municipality of Bloke|Bloke]]\n | W  = [[Municipality of Cerknica|Cerknica]]\n | NW = [[Municipality of Brezovica|Brezovica]]\n}}\n{{Velike La\u0161\u010de}}\n{{Municipalities of Slovenia}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Municipality of Velike Lasce}}\n[[Category:Municipality of Velike La\u0161\u010de| ]]\n[[Category:Municipalities of Slovenia|Velike Lasce]]\n[[Category:1998 establishments in Slovenia]]\n\n\n{{VelikeLasce-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Municipality of Velike La\u0161\u010de\n| native_name             = ''Ob\u010dina Velike La\u0161\u010de''\n| native_name_lang        = sl<!-- ISO 639-2 code e.g. \"fr\" for French. If more than one, use {{lang}} instead -->\n| settlement_type         = [[Municipalities of Slovenia|Municipality]]\n| image_skyline           = Velika Slevica.jpg\n| image_alt               =\n| image_caption           =\n| image_shield            = Velike La\u0161\u010de.png\n| shield_size             = 120x80px\n| nickname                =\n| motto                   =\n| image_map               = Obcine Slovenija 2006 Velike Lasce.svg\n| map_alt                 =\n| map_caption             = Location of the Municipality of Velike La\u0161\u010d