med Khader Almuwallad]]\n|{{flagu|Saudi Arabia}}\n|18 September 2017\n|[[Indoor athletics at the 2017 Asian Indoor and Martial Arts Games|2017 Ashgabat]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=60m Hurdles Results|url=http://ashgabat2017.com/atos/ashgabat17/resAG2017/pdf/AG2017/AT/AG2017_AT_C73A_ATM010101.pdf|website=ashgabat2017.com|date=18 September 2017|accessdate=18 September 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[High jump]]\n|rowspan=2|2.26 m\n|[[Majd Eddin Ghazal]]\n|{{flagu|Syria}}\n|rowspan=2|20 September 2017\n|rowspan=2|[[Indoor athletics at the 2017 Asian Indoor and Martial Arts Games|2017 Ashgabat]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=High Jump Results|url=http://ashgabat2017.com/atos/ashgabat17/resAG2017/pdf/AG2017/AT/AG2017_AT_C73M_ATM071101.pdf|website=ashgabat2017.com|date=20 September 2017|accessdate=25 September 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Keyvan Ghanbar Zadeh]]\n|{{flagu|Iran}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=High Jump Results|url=http://ashgabat2017.com/atos/ashgabat17/resAG2017/pdf/AG2017/AT/AG2017_AT_C73M_ATM071101.pdf|website=ashgabat2017.com|date=20 September 2017|accessdate=25 September 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Pole vault]]\n|5.60 m\n|[[Leonid Andreev (athlete)|Leonid Andreev]]\n|{{flagIOC2|UZB|2009 Asian Indoor Games}}\n|2 November 2009\n|[[Indoor athletics at the 2009 Asian Indoor Games|2009 Hanoi]]\n|\n|-\n|[[Long jump]]\n|7.96 m\n|[[Ahmed Faiz (athlete)|Ahmed Faiz]]\n|{{flagIOC2|KSA|2009 Asian Indoor Games}}\n|1 November 2009\n|[[Indoor athletics at the 2009 Asian Indoor Games|2009 Hanoi]]\n|\n|-\n|[[Triple jump]]\n|16.60 m\n|[[Roman Valiyev]]\n|{{flagIOC2|KAZ|2009 Asian Indoor Games}}\n|2 November 2009\n|[[Indoor athletics at the 2009 Asian Indoor Games|2009 Hanoi]]\n|\n|-\n|[[Shot put]]\n|19.66 m\n|[[Amin Nikfar]]\n|{{flagIOC2|IRI|2009 Asian Indoor Games}}\n|2 November 2009\n|[[Indoor athletics at the 2009 Asian Indoor Games|2009 Hanoi]]\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[Heptathlon]]\n|5791 pts\n|[[Mohammed Al-Qaree]]\n|{{flagIOC2|KSA|2009 Asian Indoor Games}}\n|1\u20132 November 2009\n|[[Indoor athle